comments: Lowry (MIA) brushes Towns' (MIN) front and marginal contact occurs as Towns starts his dribble.
Lowry (MIA) is moving alongside Towns' (MIN) path and absorbs the body contact that occurs as Towns drives inside the lane.
Lowry (MIA) raises his right arm up and initiates contact with the inside portion of Towns' (MIN) right arm, affecting his shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) initiates contact across Towns' (MIN) left arm and causes Towns to lose control of the ball during rebounding.
There is no clear and conclusive video evidence that shows if Cain's (MIA) left foot steps out of bounds as he receives the pass.

Russell (MIN) fully extends his left hand into Cain's (MIA) right hip and initiates contact that alters Cain's body trajectory as he elevates for the driving shot attempt, which is subsequently affected.
Adebayo (MIA) brushes Gobert's (MIN) right arm as Gobert back-taps the ball, and the contact is marginal.
Lowry (MIA) beats Towns (MIN) to the spot and establishes a legal guarding position prior to Towns initiating the contact at the end of the drive.
Edwards (MIN) brings his left hand forward and marginal contact occurs with Strus (MIA) as Strus elevates to save the ball back into play.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Lowry (MIA) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to the Timberwolves.
Cain (MIA) brushes McDaniels' (MIN) front and marginal contact occurs at the start of McDaniels' drive.
Adebayo (MIA) initiates contact across Gobert's (MIN) right arm during his upward shooting motion.
Russell (MIN) brings his hands forward and marginal contact occurs with Strus' (MIA) front as he turns the corner near half-court.
Russell (MIN) grasps and then quickly releases Strus' (MIA) left arm on the wing.
Strus (MIA) is bracing for the contact from Russell (MIN), and marginal contact occurs as Strus releases away from the contact.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Strus (MIA) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to the Timberwolves.
Adebayo (MIA) briefly grasps McDaniels' (MIN) arm as he cuts across the lane before immediately releasing his arm.
Gobert (MIN) and Adebayo (MIA) briefly engage and disengage as they each make contact with the ball during rebounding.
McDaniels (MIN) is turning alongside Lowry's (MIA) path and marginal body contact occurs as he defends Lowry's driving shot attempt.
Lowry (MIA) is moving alongside Russell's (MIN) path and marginal body contact occurs as Russell dribbles on the perimeter.
Adebayo (MIA) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it from Prince (MIN) as he starts his dribble.
Adebayo (MIA) is moving alongside Prince's (MIN) path and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs as Prince turns to pass.
Gobert (MIN) gathers the ball on his left foot and does not take more than two steps after his gather.
Strus (MIA) swipes down and initiates contact across Gobert's (MIN) right arm as he starts his dribble.
Cain (MIA) and Russell (MIN) engage and disengage with one another after the release of the shot attempt.

Martin (MIA) moves toward the baseline as he pursues the rebound and incidental contact occurs with Edwards (MIN) and Prince (MIN) as they come together.  The contact from Edwards then causes Prince to go out of bounds.
Prince (MIN) makes contact with the ball while he is out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to the Heat.
